Class Uri

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.server.master.common.Uri
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TavernaServerListenersREST.PropertyDescription, TavernaServerRunREST.RunDescription.ListenerList, TavernaServerSecurityREST.PermissionsDescription.LinkedPermissionDescription

    public class Uri
extends Object
    A class that makes it simpler to work with an element with a URI in an href attribute. Done with JAXB.
    Author:
    Donal Fellows
